the Yuli Spring truly is.

41
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,760
Hong Ye, look at this!

42
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,540
Miss, you have excellent taste.

43
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,920
