56
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,490
Wish-Fulfilling Rings!

57
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,830
If you land a ring,
get the prize for free!

58
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:28,360
If you miss, it's one tael of silver
for 10 rings.

59
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,830
