the Feiyu Guards

546
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:29,790
to harm his own kind

547
00:27:30,860 --> 00:27:32,840
and commit such cruel acts.

548
00:27:34,910 --> 00:27:36,840
Now that you've returned, My Lord,

549
00:27:37,110 --> 00:27:40,310
